msgid "Brightness level"
msgstr "Nivel de brillo"

#. Setting help text
msgctxt "#30001"
msgid "Level in percent of how strongly the screen remains illuminated."
msgstr "Nivel en porcentaje de qué tan intensamente permanece la pantalla iluminada."

